result.name: Kam Heung Vegetarian - Quarry Bay

reviews.text: Good variety and value for money

Three type of vegetarian foods with rice, soup and soya milk cost HKD 45

Self service, you have to fill your bowl with rice, soup and drink that enough for yourself, no wasting is allowed.

We couldn't find the place so we called the restaurant.  The owner had someone come get us at the nearby McDonald's.  The food was excellent and very reasonably priced.  They were very accommodating and made sure we knew there's egg in one of the noodles.   For the price of 45 HKD (43?), you pick 3 items AND you get soup, congee, rice, noodles and soy milk.
Cheap and tasty, friendly staff
Love it.
